mess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-1.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1730313747197\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat kind of alcohol is Midori? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eMidori is a Japanese melon flavored liqueur made from Japanese muskmelons and yubari fruit. These are infused in neutral grain spirits. After that, they are blended with brandy and sugar and the addition of green food coloring to make Midori.\u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1730313766208\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is a Midori Sour made of? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eMidori, vodka, lemon juice, lime juice and club soda (or lemon-lime soda). \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/midori-sour/?tp_image_id=132824\" data-pin-title=\"Midori Sour\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-3.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-3-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Midori-Sour-Recipe.-1-3-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeau